Package: getdns
Type: Package
Title: Query Domain Name System Using the 'getdns' Application Programming Interface
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2018-01-25
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5670-2640"))
  )
Maintainer: Bob Rudis <bob@rud.is>
Description: The core library used is 'getdns' which is an implementation of a
    modern asynchronous 'DNS' 'API'; the specification was originally edited by 
    'Paul Hoffman'. It is intended to make all types of DNS information easily 
    available to application developers and non-'DNS' experts.
URL: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/getdns
BugReports: https://github.com/hrbrmstr/getdns/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
